64
00:06:31,096 --> 00:06:32,806
Mengenai kritikan pula,

65
00:06:33,515 --> 00:06:35,642
saya tak ambil peduli tentangnya.

66
00:06:36,226 --> 00:06:38,896
Seseorang pernah berkata,
"Cara balas dendam terbaik

67
00:06:39,897 --> 00:06:42,441
terhadap orang busuk hati
adalah jangan beri perhatian."

68
00:06:43,484 --> 00:06:46,403
Saya tak nak beri perhatian
untuk balas dendam kepada mereka.

69
00:06:46,487 --> 00:06:47,738
Saya dah jawab soalan awak?

70
00:06:49,490 --> 00:06:50,449
Ya.

71
00:06:52,576 --> 00:06:54,203
Dia kata saya busuk hati?

72
00:06:54,286 --> 00:06:56,914
Ya. Kenapa awak tanya dia soalan itu?.

73
00:06:57,706 --> 00:06:58,999
- Cis.
- Soalan seterusnya.

74
00:06:59,082 --> 00:07:01,043
- Saya ada soalan!
- Saya!

75
00:07:01,126 --> 00:07:02,461
Lelaki berbaju petak.

76
00:07:02,544 --> 00:07:03,879
Lelaki itu. Ya.

77
00:07:05,881 --> 00:07:09,343
Saya Lee Seong-hun
saya nak buka perniagaan sendiri.

78
00:07:10,844 --> 00:07:11,970
Selamat sejahtera.

79
00:07:12,596 --> 00:07:14,306
Nama saya Seo Dal-mi.

80
00:07:24,024 --> 00:07:24,900
Seo Dal-mi?

81
00:07:26,777 --> 00:07:28,320
Kenapa? Awak kenal dia?

82
00:07:28,403 --> 00:07:29,446
Apa?

83
00:07:30,197 --> 00:07:31,323
Tidak.

84
00:07:35,452 --> 00:07:37,871
Ya. Sila tanya.

85
00:07:38,872 --> 00:07:41,959
Awak dah buat banyak keputusan hebat
dalam hidup awak.

86
00:07:42,751 --> 00:07:44,795
Tolong jujur dengan kami.

87
00:07:45,462 --> 00:07:48,924
Ada tak keputusan pentingkan diri,
Cik Seo In-jae?

88
00:07:51,176 --> 00:07:52,386
Apa masalah dia?

89
00:07:52,970 --> 00:07:54,596
Seo In-jae? Bukankah Won In-jae?

90
00:07:55,264 --> 00:07:56,431
Dia tukar nama keluarga?

91
00:07:56,515 --> 00:07:58,767
- Dia anti?
- Mungkin saling mengenali.

92
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:06,775
Mestilah ada. Saya pun manusia.

93
00:08:07,776 --> 00:08:11,780
Mungkin ia buat saya nampak materialistik,
tapi ia perlu dilakukan.

94
00:08:12,573 --> 00:08:13,657
Tapi Cik Seo Dal-mi.

95
00:08:14,908 --> 00:08:16,159
Nama saya ialah…

96
00:08:21,832 --> 00:08:23,083
Won In-jae.

