00:09:01,788 --> 00:09:05,792
Kakak pun patut pergi menari sekali.
Seronok main bersama.

105
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:08,754
Kakak lebih suka Pump
daripada Pentas Menari.

106
00:09:08,837 --> 00:09:12,007
Yakah? Saya pun akan main Pump
mulai hari ini.

107
00:09:14,843 --> 00:09:17,638
Kenapa tulis surat letak jawatan
setiap hari macam diari?

108
00:09:17,721 --> 00:09:19,640
Janganlah begini. Dengarlah cakap saya.

109
00:09:19,723 --> 00:09:21,975
Saya ada rancangan perniagaan yang baik.

110
00:09:22,059 --> 00:09:23,727
Itu pasti akan buat kita kebuluran.

111
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:28,357
Kakak, kita patut hentikan
pergaduhan mereka, bukan?

112
00:09:28,857 --> 00:09:32,653
Saya bekerja macam hamba selama 20 tahun
di syarikat orang!

113
00:09:33,403 --> 00:09:36,073
Biarlah saya buat sesuatu
yang saya nak sekarang!

114
00:09:38,325 --> 00:09:40,744
Kalau awak berhenti,
awak hilang sumber pendapatan.

115
00:09:40,827 --> 00:09:43,955
Ini yang akan terjadi.
Mati kesejukan atau kelaparan.

116
00:09:44,539 --> 00:09:46,708
Saya tak nak anak-anak saya kebuluran!

117
00:09:47,209 --> 00:09:48,251
Jadi…

118
00:09:52,589 --> 00:09:55,425
Kalau awak nak berhenti bekerja,
kita perlu bercerai dulu.

119
00:09:59,513 --> 00:10:01,723
- A-hyeon.
- Ambillah.

120
00:10:02,724 --> 00:10:03,725
Ambil surat ini!

121
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,774
SEO IN-JAE

122
00:10:13,944 --> 00:10:18,073
Nenek. Nenek tolonglah hentikan
pergaduhan mereka.

123
00:10:18,156 --> 00:10:19,699
Ayah dengar cakap nenek.

124
00:10:20,325 --> 00:10:21,701
Kalau nenek buat sesuatu…

125
00:10:21,785 --> 00:10:24,663
Mereka takkan berkahwin
kalau ayah kamu dengar cakap nenek.

126
00:10:25,997 --> 00:10:26,998
Nah.

127
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:32,671
Bolehkah nenek tinggal dengan kami?

128
00:10:32,754 --> 00:10:35,257
Lupakan. Mereka bergaduh
lebih teruk kalau nenek ada.

129
00:10:37,300 --> 00:10:38,343
Oh, ya.

130
00:10:39,761 --> 00:10:43,473
In-jae. Ini untuk kamu.
Mereka minta nenek berikan kepada kamu.

131
00:10:43,557 --> 00:10:46,059
Nenek, kenapa beri sekarang?

132
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:48,562
Bila lagi nak beri? Esok?

133
00:10:48,645 --> 00:10:50,105
Tak tahu bersyukur langsung.

134
00:10:50,188 --> 00:10:51,231
Untunglah kakak.

135
00:10:52,983 --> 00:10:56,153
Tolong buang, nenek.
Mereka tak putus asa lagi?

136
00:10:56,236 --> 00:10:58,530
Boleh dapat hadiah
kalau rajin belajar begini.

137
00:10:58,613 --> 00:10:59,906
- Awak ditolak.
- Tak apa.

138
00:10:59,990 --> 00:11:01,741
Dia suruh buang. Dah ditolak.

139
00:11:03,118 --> 00:11:06,204
- Ada ramai gadis di dunia ini. Tak apa.
- Saya carikan lagi.

140
00:11:06,288 --> 00:11:07,581
Tengoklah dia.

141
00:11:14,045 --> 00:11:15,338
Kamu nak apa?

142
00:11:15,422 --> 00:11:16,965
HAN JI-PYEONG

143
00:11:17,048 --> 00:11:18,258
Saya tak lapar.

144
00:11:26,892 --> 00:11:29,102
- Saya pergi ke sekolah dulu, nenek.
- Okey.

145
00:11:29,186 --> 00:11:30,854
- Saya pergi ke sekolah dulu!
- Okey.

146
00:11:33,857 --> 00:11:35,233
Kenapa?

147
00:11:37,861 --> 00:11:40,739
Kakak, jom naik bas seterusnya.

148
00:11:40,822 --> 00:11:42,365
Tak boleh! Kita kena ikut ayah.

149
00:11:42,449 --> 00:11:44,367
Ayah? Kenapa nak ikut ayah?

150
00:11:44,451 --> 00:11:46,912
Mereka akan bercerai
kalau ayah letak jawatan.

151
00:11:46,995 --> 00:11:48,914
Mari halang ayah. Nak hidup berasingan?

152
00:11:49,998 --> 00:11:51,791
- Tak nak.
- Jom.

153
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,390
SYARIKAT PEMBINAAN
DAN PERDAGANGAN ILCHEUNG

154
00:12:26,701 --> 00:12:27,536
Apa ini?

155
00:12:31,414 --> 00:12:32,541
Saya bayar kamu semua

156
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,753
berpuluh-puluh juta won setiap tahun.

157
00:12:37,379 --> 00:12:39,506
Tapi kamu semua tikam saya dari belakang?

158
00:12:40,257 --> 00:12:42,676
Siapa yang bayar kamu semua?

159
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:44,719
Saya atau pengurus cawangan?

160
00:12:44,803 --> 00:12:46,555
Jangan buat begini, encik.

161
00:12:49,975 --> 00:12:52,269
Jangan cuba menyampuk.

162
00:12:54,854 --> 00:12:57,357
Awak yang berkomplot
dengan para pengurus cawangan

163
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,067
untuk tipu mengenai hasil jualan?

164
00:12:59,818 --> 00:13:01,528
Padahal awak ambil duit saya!

165
00:13:01,611 --> 00:13:04,030
- Ayah.
- Awak tikam saya dari belakang!

166
00:13:04,614 --> 00:13:06,449
Berani awak buat begitu?

167
00:13:08,743 --> 00:13:10,745
Samanlah saya kalau awak nak.

168
00:13:10,829 --> 00:13:13,582
Tak. Kita boleh buat perjanjian dulu.

169
00:13:13,665 --> 00:13:15,166
Berapa awak nak?

170
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:17,919
Berapa awak nak?

171
00:13:18,503 --> 00:13:19,629
Berapa?

172
00:13:30,098 --> 00:13:31,224
<i>Ayah kena pukul?</i>

173
00:13:31,308 --> 00:13:35,520
Ya. Jadi, apabila ayah kata nak buka
perniagaan sendiri,

174
00:13:35,604 --> 00:13:37,355
mak patut bersetuju.

175
00:13:38,273 --> 00:13:41,318
Betul. Kasihan ayah.

176
00:13:41,902 --> 00:13:43,945
- Berapa dia nak beri?
- Apa?

177
00:13:44,029 --> 00:13:45,864
Dia kata nak bayar, bukan?

178
00:13:46,448 --> 00:13:47,741
Berapa dia nak beri?

179
00:13:48,283 --> 00:13:49,492
Dia beri sepuluh juta won?

180
00:13:50,076 --> 00:13:52,621
Mak, adakah duit lebih penting sekarang?

181
00:13:53,413 --> 00:13:55,790
Ya. Duit penting untuk mak.

182
00:13:55,874 --> 00:13:57,626
Walau apa pun, duit paling penting.

183
00:13:57,709 --> 00:14:00,253
Macam mana nak bayar yuran sekolah
kalau ayah berhenti?

184
00:14:00,337 --> 00:14:02,839
In-jae, kamu kena berhenti
semua kelas tuisyen.

185
00:14:03,423 --> 00:14:05,800
Nak belajar di rumah
walau kawan kamu pergi tuisyen?

186
00:14:05,884 --> 00:14:08,053
Nak duduk di rumah
apabila ada lawatan sekolah?

187
00:14:13,642 --> 00:14:15,268
Kamu ada masa depan yang cerah.

188
00:14:16,269 --> 00:14:18,104
Ayah kamu kena bekerja walau dipukul.

189
00:14:19,189 --> 00:14:20,315
Itu tugas dia.

190
00:14:27,322 --> 00:14:28,531
Ayah.

191
00:14:28,615 --> 00:14:30,325
AYAM

192
00:14:33,244 --> 00:14:34,162
Maafkan saya.

193
00:14:38,917 --> 00:14:40,043
Kita patut bercerai.

194
00:14:41,002 --> 00:14:42,212
- Ayah!
- Ayah!

195
00:14:46,216 --> 00:14:48,218
Baiklah. Kita akan bercerai.

196
00:14:51,054 --> 00:14:52,597
In-jae dan Dal-mi.

197
00:14:53,765 --> 00:14:55,183
Kamu nak tinggal dengan siapa?

198
00:14:56,726 --> 00:14:59,229
Kamu nak ikut mak atau ayah?

199
